    <item>
      <title>尼康披露 EssilorLuxottica 持有 5% 股份后股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/nikon-s-shares-surge-after-revealing-essilorluxottica-s-5-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼康公司披露法国眼镜制造商 EssilorLuxottica SA 已收购 ASML Holding NV 的日本竞争对手 EssilorLuxottica SA 5.1% 的股份后，其股价创下两个月来最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/nikon-s-shares-surge-after-revealing-essilorluxottica-s-5-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:55:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>社交媒体纷争导致 Ola Electric 首次公开募股 (IPO) 收益迅速消退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ola-electric-s-big-ipo-gains-fading-fast-amid-social-media-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最大的电动滑板车制造商 Ola Electric Mobility Ltd. 的股价周一暴跌，原因是其首席执行官与一位单口相声演员在网上发生争吵，加剧了人们对该公司产品的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ola-electric-s-big-ipo-gains-fading-fast-amid-social-media-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:53:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>历峰集团将 Yoox Net-A-Porter 出售给德国 Mytheresa</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/richemont-finally-offloads-yoox-net-a-porter-to-german-rival</link>
      <description><![CDATA[历峰集团同意将其陷入困境的在线时尚业务 Yoox Net-A-Porter 出售给 Mytheresa，以换取这家德国电子商务公司的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/richemont-finally-offloads-yoox-net-a-porter-to-german-rival</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:20:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受北京刺激计划传闻影响，中国芯片股上涨 130 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chinese-chip-stocks-gain-13-billion-on-talk-of-beijing-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国顶级芯片制造商中芯国际引领该行业 130 亿美元的上涨，此前投资者押注北京方面将对其地缘政治野心的核心行业宣布更多政策或财政支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chinese-chip-stocks-gain-13-billion-on-talk-of-beijing-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 04:22:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球投资者纷纷囤积现金，押注台湾人工智能回归</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/global-investors-are-hoarding-cash-to-bet-on-taiwan-ai-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外国投资者在台湾拥有数十亿美元的现金，这对于预测近期市场下跌将是短暂的股市多头来说是一个令人鼓舞的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/global-investors-are-hoarding-cash-to-bet-on-taiwan-ai-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 03:51:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>iPhone 制造商鸿海收入持续反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/iphone-maker-hon-hai-sustains-revenue-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司的主要制造合作伙伴台湾鸿海精密工业股份有限公司（又名富士康）报告称，上季度销售额增长 20%，超过平均预期。Annabelle Droulers 在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/iphone-maker-hon-hai-sustains-revenue-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 02:33:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特基金表示愿意增持任天堂股份，股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/nintendo-shares-jump-after-saudi-fund-says-open-to-bigger-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯主权财富基金一位高管向当地媒体表示，该基金正考虑增持日本游戏公司的股份，此后，任天堂股价一度上涨 3.9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/nintendo-shares-jump-after-saudi-fund-says-open-to-bigger-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 01:01:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果逐渐放弃每年发布新品的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-06/when-will-apple-intelligence-be-released-when-is-apple-releasing-m4-macs-ipad-m1xksx7q</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果正在逐渐远离其年度产品升级周期，此举可能导致发布频率更高，延迟现象减少。此外：让我们看看该公司的下一代产品何时上市，包括 Apple Intelligence。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-06/when-will-apple-intelligence-be-released-when-is-apple-releasing-m4-macs-ipad-m1xksx7q</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 12:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
